QueryText: Farmer needs information regarding control measures for fungal attack in garlic  Crop ?

QueryText: Farmer wants to know information about weed management in wheat crop?

QueryText: Farmer wants to know Information about Regarding Fungal disease ( Yellow leaf)  of garlic  crop  ?

QueryText: Farmer needs information regarding control measures for root rot in garlic Crop?

QueryText: Farmer wants to know information about dosage of Trichoderma viridi 5% in garlic crop?

QueryText: Farmer wants information how to get better quality bulb in garlic crop ?
KccAns: लहसुन  फसल में बेहतर गुणवत्ता वाले फल प्राप्त करने के लिए आप सूक्ष्म पोषक तत्वों का कॉन्बिनेशन (agromin max)जिसमें मैंगनीज (एमएन), 5% जिंक (Zn.) 5.3% कॉपर (सीयू), 2.4% मोलिब्डेनम (मो), 0.1% बोरॉन (बी), 1.0% (agromin max) का उपयोग कर सकते हैं 25 ग्राम प्रति पंप के हिसाब से उपयोग करें

QueryText: Farmer want to know information about  how to increase growth of  Garlic crop ?

QueryText: Farmer want to information about nano urea dose in wheat crop  ?
